    <p>Basically Pokemon Go but with more focus on combat and equipment system. I am creating this game as a university project, however I do plan on still developing it after the semester is over.</p>
    <p>The game is being written in Xamarin.Forms. Yes, I am aware that it is not exactly the best tool for creating games, but as the focus of the game is on combat and equipment it is not that bad.</p>
